{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Step into the whimsical world full of action, humor... and TRASH with Bumpkin &amp; Sprout! Bring along your good mood and a touch of courage. These two carefree mushrooms must engage in an uneven battle against the nefarious Pollution Spirit to save themselves and Mother Nature. Will they succeed? It all depends on you!</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611600/extras/Anim_01.gif?t=1731626215\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bumpkin &amp; Sprout is a new 3D platform game suitable for both young and old players. In this game, you take on the role of a spirited mushroom embarking on a journey to rescue their friend from the Pollution Spirit. Along the way, our hero faces off against trashy monsters while aiding Nature in the quest to preserve the environment. They also uncover the history of Nature's struggle against the Pollution Spirit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611600/extras/Anim_03.gif?t=1731626215\" />The game's adventure begins in a forest filled with waste. A world once guarded by Nature is now plunged into chaos and on the brink of destruction. Only by convincing the Pollution Spirit to return to the side of good can the environment still be saved from its negative impact on nature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611600/extras/Anim_02.gif?t=1731626215\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is designed for everyone. A balanced difficulty level ensures that both children and adults will have a fantastic time. An absorbing story, a fantastical reality, and humor are the distinguishing features of the latest game from Rabid Rat.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store